{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回 飞大夫的脚\n\n本章主要讲述风四娘与飞大夫的重逢以及围绕萧十一郎展开的谜团。\n\n风四娘在山崖上目睹飞大夫以两指夹断刺客长剑的绝世武功，随后现身与这位老友叙旧。飞大夫双腿已被萧十一郎齐膝砍断，住处石墓中的棺材也被人偷走。风四娘受托追查偷棺贼，在荒山中发现一个被倒吊的男子，此人穿着与偷棺贼相同的珠花皮靴，却自称姓萧。风四娘识破其伪装后，该男子吞毒自尽。萧十一郎暗中将棺材送回，并吊起偷棺贼留给风四娘追查。本章揭示了风四娘对萧十一郎多年的暗恋之情，以及萧十一郎堂堂正正的人格特质，同时埋下偷棺贼背后势力的伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "原来是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "一别多年，想不到公孙先生风采依然如昔，武功却更精进了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "四娘对老朽如此客气，莫非是有求而来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "我若对人客气，人家就说我是有求而来的，我若对人不客气，人家就说我无礼，唉，这年头做人可真不容易。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "其实我只不过是经过此地，忽然想到来看看你，无论如何，我们总算是老朋友了，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "你看，我既没有生气，也没有受伤，为何要来求你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "现在你已看过了我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "看过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "很好，再见。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "果然是条老狐狸，谁也骗不了你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "遇着你这女妖怪，我也只好做做老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "你可知道这两人是谁？为何要杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "老夫一生纵横天下，杀人无算，别人要来杀我，也是天经地义的事，我又何苦要去追问他们的来历。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "我早就知道你不怕死，但你若被一些后生小子不明不白的杀了，岂非冤枉得很，你难道不怕一世英名扫地？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你究竟想要我怎样？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "你若肯帮我一个忙，我就帮你将仇家打听出来，你总该知道打听消息是我的拿手本事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我早就知道你找我绝不会有什么好事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "但这次却是件好事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "不但是好事，而且还是件大事，事成之后，你我都有好处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我本来也很愿意助你一臂之力，只可惜你来迟了一步。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "来迟了一步？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "自然是被人砍断的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "是谁下的毒手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "我不想找他，你们为何偏偏要我去找他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你本该去找他的，只要有他相助，何愁大事不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "你呢？你不想找他复仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他虽然伤了我，我却并不怨他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "好，你既不肯说，我就送你回去吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不必。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "谁说不必，你这样子怎么能上得了山？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "男女授受不亲，不敢劳动大驾，四娘你请便吧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "什么男女授受不亲，我从来也没有将自己当做女人，从来也不管这一套。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这绝不是他做的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "他本来的确不穿这种靴子的，但鬼知道他现在已变成什么样子了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎永远不会变的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "这倒真是怪事，他砍断了你的两条腿，你反而帮他说好话。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他堂堂正正的来找我，堂堂正正的伤了我，我知道他是个堂堂正正的人，绝不做鬼鬼祟祟的事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "这么样说来，你好像比我还了解他了。可是，这孩子临死前为什么要说出他的名字来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这孩子不认得萧十一郎，但你却认得他的，你若追着那凶手，就可查出他是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "说来说去，原来你是想要我去替你追贼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "好，我就替你去追，但追不追得上，我就不敢说了，你总该知道我的轻功并不太高明。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那人背着口棺材，必定走不快的，否则这孩子就不至于死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为何要冒十一郎的名？为何要杀这孩子？否则就算偷了八百口棺材，我也绝不会去追他的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你是不是中了别人的暗算？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是强盗……强盗……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你遇着了强盗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "我看你自己倒有些像强盗，我若救了你，说不定反被你抢上一票。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只要姑娘肯出手相救，我必有重谢。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你既已被强盗抢了，还能用什么来谢我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "我怎么看你这人都不像好东西，但我却也不能见死不救。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "谢谢……谢谢……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "我也不要你谢我，只要我救了你之后，你莫要在我身上打歪主意就好了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "姑娘既已答应相救，为什么还不动手？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "我想来想去，还是觉得有些不妥。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "有什么不妥？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "我一个妇道人家，做事不能不分外仔细，现在半夜三更的，四下又没有人，我救了你之后，你万一要是……要是起了恶心，我怎么办？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "姑娘请放心，我绝不是个坏人，何况，瞧姑娘所施展上树的身法，也绝不是好欺负的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "但我还是小心些好，总得先问你几件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你要问什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "不知道你贵姓呀，是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我姓萧，从口北来的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "害你的那强盗，是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不瞒姑娘说，我连他的人影都没有看见，就已被他吊了起来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你偷来的那口棺材呢？也被他黑吃黑了么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "什么棺材？姑娘说的话，我完全不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？为何要打我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "我正要问你，你究竟是什么人？为何要偷飞大夫的棺材？是谁主使你来的？假冒十一郎的名是何用心？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你不肯说，是不是？好，那么我告诉你，我就是风四娘，落在我手上的人，没有一个能不说实话的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "风四娘，原来你就是那风四娘！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你既然听过我的名字，总该知道我说的话不假。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "想不到今日竟遇上了你这女妖怪，好，好，好，好……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "倒吊男子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你现在还有法子让我说话么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_dao_diao_nan_zi",
      "text": "你死了也好，反正你说不说都和我全无关系。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "这棺材怎会回来的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "自然是有人送回来的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "萧十一郎？又是他！原来那人就是被他吊起来的！奇怪他为何不追问那人的来历呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他知道，有些人的来历是问也问不出的！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "那么，他为何还要将那人留在那里？难道是故意留给我的吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "他的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "他既然知道我在这里，为何不等我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我说你不愿见他，他只好走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "不错，我一见这人就有气……他到哪里去了呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你既不愿见他，又何必问他到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "text": "你这老狐狸，我希望他再来砍断你的两只手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_da_fu",
      "speaker_name": "飞大夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三十多岁的女人还像个孩子，这倒也真是怪事……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    }
